{"tid":1129211,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"杜生事件分析","createTime":"2019-04-28T10:51:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T00:55:00.000Z","uid":28181,"like":11,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e3e0201a7dd7686b95f94c644fe69f5ba0d39544","tid":1129211,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T10:51:36.000Z","msg":"<strong>先從結論講起：</strong><br />\n成件事係杜生拖糧3個月，但之後個d咩偽造文書純粹係誤會。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>時間線推論：</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">4月24日</span> 杜生公司入數比程小姐，但無通資番程小姐<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">4月26日</span> 程小姐受訪指控杜生公司拖糧仲未出<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">4月27日</span> 訪問出左街，驚動杜生check番條數見到張入數紙寫4-4-2019（其實係24-4-2019，但個2字無左色）於是叫職員同程小姐講4-4-2019出左糧。程小姐反問10號先比戶口，4號點出糧？杜生公司再仔細檢查張入數紙發現原來個2字無左色，係24號入數，唔係4號，於是豪仔回：「24號，個2字無左色」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>動機推論：</strong><br />\n無論4號定24號入數，拖糧係拖左幾個月，無動機由24號改做4號。<br />\n24號係程小姐訪問出街之前既日子，「比人唱先出糧」既說法不成立。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KuVatya.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKuVatya.png&h=7c86f910&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qRZyrjQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqRZyrjQ.png&h=c7cb1f13&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/71XoOyb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F71XoOyb.png&h=64f3a671&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c2492500c8171e51005b2d5139cb7084cd545e7","tid":1129211,"uid":238644,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T11:15:28.000Z","msg":"拖糧就拖糧啦，仲阿趦阿趄。"},{"pid":"726d25476b165c8f3abdcf08ce46601e9d1988fc","tid":1129211,"uid":121247,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T11:16:52.000Z","msg":"邊位杜生？ 恒大杜sir我就識"},{"pid":"f96b51c2608000150ca7e4fde28d6958feada491","tid":1129211,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T11:20:14.000Z","msg":"一般節目出街後先找數<br />\n最後一個節目係3月18號出街<br />\n不過出街後幾耐要找就無人知"},{"pid